review.reviewBody: very tasty broth, generous portions, fresh food, will definitely order again. well worth the money.
Best wonton soup in town & tasty spring rolls. Sandwiches are a great value too.
Best pho I've ever had. Hands down. lean thin strips of beef in the rare steak pho. flavourful broth doesn't even need hoison. always follows instructions to a T. My favourite!
Delicious chicken pho, fresh and crispy pork spring rolls with excellent flavour and sauce on the side. Generous portions. Awesome value and definitely the best pho in South Surrey!

food is delish and great service. I requested vegi spring roll substitute as I don't eat pork and they are so yummy. The coconut juice has real coconut and is always a favorite. Everything we ordered is great!
